<h2 class=story-heading>SMS for Appointment Reminders</h2>

<p class=story>Patients failing to attend their scheduled doctor visits contribute to inefficiencies and misused resources. In general it is found that a reminder, whether it be by text or phone, is helpful in improving attendance, however SMS technology is a more cost-effective approach.</p>

