<h2 class=story-heading>SMS for Education</h2>

<p class=story>SMS text-based education is emerging as an effective way to engage patients in better self-care. Lack of education around basic health information leads to approximately $106 billion to $238 billion in economic burden each year18.  Text message outreach with educational content can be an efficient way to improve patients’ health literacy.</p>

